Wewe - umefanya mengi kupigana na adui yako, wale wanao pigana na wewe, kujaribu kufanya mambo ya kila aina....

0:17:29.660,0:17:33.360
Watu wanakusanifu, nawe unawasanifu.

0:17:33.360,0:17:37.040
Unawapeleka mahakamani, unawafunga gerezani

0:17:37.040,0:17:41.220
Waume Wengi wa watu waliopo hapa, wamo gerezani

0:17:41.220,0:17:45.200
Wake wengi wa watu mliopo hapa, wamo gerezani.

0:17:45.200,0:17:50.000
Majirani zenu wengi ninyi mliopo hapa, wamo gerezani

0:17:50.000,0:17:57.260
Wengi wenu ninyi mliopo hapa leo mmewafunga wafanyakazi wenzenu mliofanya nao kazi.

0:17:57.260,0:18:02.060
Ukiangalia nyuma katika yale mliyoyafanya...

0:18:02.060,0:18:05.500
Wengi mmewafunga wakombozi wenu wa kesho.

0:18:05.500,0:18:11.500
Mwambie jirani yako, "wengi wamewafunga wakombozi wao wa kesho -

0:18:11.500,0:18:14.220
kwa sababu ya makosa."

0:18:14.220,0:18:20.900
Kwa sababu ya kosa alilolifanya mtu sasa, wamewafunga wakombozi wao

0:18:20.900,0:18:28.860
Mtu uliyemfunga ni mwokozi wako wa kesho, na yumo gerezani.

0:18:28.860,0:18:35.200
Jichunguze, wafanyakazi wenzio -
 walichofanya ni kibaya - tunakubali

0:18:35.200,0:18:45.560
Wanaweza wakawa wamefanya uhalifu; kuiba, uharibifu katika kampuni yako, lakini wewe umewahukumu kifo,

0:18:45.560,0:18:49.800
au gerezani - baadhi yao hata kifo.

0:18:49.800,0:18:55.800
Lakini hawa ni watu ambao Mungu anataka kuwatumia kama wakombozi wako kesho

0:18:55.800,0:19:01.640
haijalishi nu ubaya wa namna gani, huyo mtu ni sasa.

0:19:01.640,0:19:10.780
Kesho ni kitu usichokielewa, siri usiyoielewa.

0:19:10.780,0:19:19.580
Lakini kwa sababu unadai haki yako, "Oh hapana, mtu huyu alinitukana, aliniaibisha, aliiba mali yangu" -

0:19:19.580,0:19:22.600
unamhukumu aende gerezani.

0:19:22.600,0:19:27.060
Mtu huyo huyo ndiye mwokozi wako kesho.

0:19:27.060,0:19:30.300
Utakosa mkombozi kesho, lakini yupo kule.

0:19:30.300,0:19:34.420
Inaweza kuwa mkombozi kwa watoto wako kesho.

0:19:34.420,0:19:43.240
Hii ndio maana Biblia inasema, "Samehe wale waliotukosea"...

0:19:43.240,0:19:45.760
Unataka kusema, "Baba, Nisamehe".

0:19:45.760,0:19:50.920
Wewe umewasamehe wale waliokukosea?

0:19:50.920,0:19:53.400
Unasema, "Utusamehe, kama sisi nasi tunavyowasamehe wale ambao wamefanyaje"?

0:19:53.400,0:19:54.620
[Waliotukosea.]

0:19:54.620,0:19:57.980
Hivi ndivyo niliyomaanisha.

0:19:57.980,0:20:02.020
Baba, utusamehe, kama sisi tunavyowasamehe wale ambao wame...

0:20:02.020,0:20:05.520
Sharti ni: unatakiwa kuwasamehe kabla Hajakusamehe.

0:20:05.520,0:20:10.220
Sharti ni: watu hawa wana makosa leo...

0:20:10.220,0:20:13.260
Hata Biblia katika kitabu cha Wagalatia imesema;

0:20:13.260,0:20:19.940
Ikiwa mmemshika mtu akitenda dhambi au amekosea...

0:20:19.940,0:20:29.980
Mmemshika mtu anaiba - inasema kwamba mumrejeshe mtu huyo kwa upole.

0:20:29.980,0:20:38.880
Kumrejesha mtu ni kumshauri, kuzungumza na mtu huyo, si kumhukumu.

0:20:38.880,0:20:44.080
Kwa sababu ukihukumu, nani atakayekuhukumu wewe siku ya mwisho?

0:20:44.080,0:20:47.940
Kama kuna kitu ninakiogopa sana....

0:20:47.940,0:20:50.540
Wakiuliza, "T.B. Joshua, unaogopa kitu gani zaidi"?

0:20:50.540,0:20:53.560
Kesho.

0:20:53.560,0:20:58.360
Ninaposema kesho namaanisha "yajayo".

0:20:58.360,0:21:02.220
Ninapogeuka naikabili kesho.

0:21:02.220,0:21:04.280
Hivi ndivyo ninavyomaanisha.

0:21:04.280,0:21:05.240
Naogopa.

0:21:05.240,0:21:08.300
Sina hofu ya kile ninachokiona sasa.

0:21:08.300,0:21:12.120
Naogopa kile nitakachokiona baadaye.

0:21:12.120,0:21:18.900
Unaimiliki sasa, lakini Mungu anamiliki mustakabali wetu.

0:21:18.900,0:21:24.520
Ibada ya Jumapili SCOAN

0:21:24.520,0:21:32.400
Unaweza kusema kwa Mungu, "Tafadhali, niache".

0:21:32.400,0:21:39.160
Lakini "wakati ujao" yuko pale kwa ajili yako ahukumu matendo unayoyaonesha sasa.

0:21:39.160,0:21:50.500
Sasa, ukimuona Yesu, unaweza kumpiga kofi, lakini "wakati ujao" yuko pale kukuhukumu.

0:21:50.500,0:21:54.300
Kama kuna kitu nakiogopa - ni "wakati ujao".

0:21:54.300,0:21:57.740
Sitatumia neno "baadaye", nitasema "wakati ujao"

0:21:57.740,0:22:01.440
Kama kuna kitu naogopa - wakati ujao.

0:22:01.440,0:22:02.640
Mwambie jirani yako.

0:22:02.640,0:22:06.820
[Kama kuna naogopa - wakati ujao]

0:22:06.820,0:22:09.740
Nauogopa "wakati ujao"

0:22:09.740,0:22:14.680
Sawa, wewe - naijua hofu, lakini wakati ujao...

0:22:14.680,0:22:17.340
Kwa sababu ya hofu hii - kama ukinigonga, nitakaa kimya tu.

0:22:17.340,0:22:25.480
Kwa sababu sijui; kama wewe ni mbaya zaidi sasa, labda baadaye utakuwa pamoja nami.

0:22:25.480,0:22:26.480
Nimetenda dhambi.

0:22:26.480,0:22:35.380
Mwangalie Paulo mwangalie Sauli...

0:22:35.380,0:22:42.440
Umemwona mtumishi wako ofisini; baadaye anakuwa kiongozi.

0:22:42.440,0:22:55.180
Umumwona mtu aliyetoka kijijini kwenu, umempokea, umemlaza, umemvisha, umemhudumia,

0:22:55.180,0:23:00.680
na kisha, kabla hujajua, anakuwa Meneja Mkuu wa kampuni,

0:23:00.680,0:23:05.440
mtu ambaye watoto wako wanamkimbilia kwa ajili ya kupata msaada.

0:23:05.440,0:23:12.900
Mvulana mdogo au msichana ambaye alikuja kutoka kijijini, na wewe ulikuwa kama baba yake mjini - umempokea

0:23:12.900,0:23:14.700
kwa sababu ni familia yako.

0:23:14.700,0:23:17.260
Unamuuliza anapotaka kuishi.

0:23:17.260,0:23:25.040
Unaanza kumtumia kama msichana au mvulana wa kazi, mlinzi au vyovyote vile...

0:23:25.040,0:23:29.120
Kabla hujajua, anaanza shule.

0:23:29.120,0:23:39.040
Muda unavyokwenda, kabla hujajua, anakuwa kiongozi, gavana, rais...

0:23:39.040,0:23:43.480
Sasa, yuko pale kukusaidia pamoja na familia yako.

0:23:43.480,0:23:52.000
Ibada ya Jumapili SCOAN

0:23:52.000,0:24:01.680
Sasa, unaanza kulalamika; Nenda kaonane naye. Nilmkaribisha alipokuja Lagos kutoka kijijini

0:24:01.680,0:24:06.020
Nilimvisha, nilimpeleka shule. Nenda kaonane naye

0:24:06.020,0:24:16.320
Sasa, unakuwa shujaa wa maombi, unaomba; "Mungu, huyu mvulana - Peter, nilimkaribisha, nilimpokea, nilimvika

0:24:16.320,0:24:24.900
Nilimpeleka shule. Sasa ni milionea. Mungu, nakwenda ofisini kwake sasa kuonana naye. Chochote nitakachosema -

0:24:24.900,0:24:29.480
Mungu, ingia moyoni mwake".

0:24:29.480,0:24:35.840
Mungu anatakiwa aingie moyoni mwake - ili nitakapoongea anisikilize. Nahitaji Dola milioni moja.

0:24:35.840,0:24:40.960
Lazima asaini cheki kwa ajili yangu.

0:24:40.960,0:24:43.700
Unafunga kabla ya kwenda kwake.

0:24:43.700,0:24:48.260
Unaelekea ofisini, unataka kuingia ofisini...

0:24:48.260,0:24:55.080
Unajua, kabla ya kuonana na Meneja mkuu au kiongozi kuna itifaki zinazotakiwa kufuatwa.

0:24:55.080,0:25:00.340
Kwanza, mlinzi atakuambia ukae chini.

0:25:00.340,0:25:03.920
Wakati umekaa, unaanza kuongea na mlinzi: - "Habari gani"

0:25:03.920,0:25:04.520
- "Salama"

0:25:04.520,0:25:12.620
-. "Ni mwanangu. Alipokuja kutoka kijijini ni mimi niliye...

0:25:12.620,0:25:18.780
... ni mimi niliyemkaribisha na kumpokea miaka ya 90s... "

0:25:18.780,0:25:22.440
Na mlinzi anashangazwa, "Ulimpokea?''

0:25:22.440,0:25:32.840
Kama una baadhi ya picha nzuri ambazo alikuwa mdogo sana, unawaonesha huku ukifafanua,

0:25:32.840,0:25:38.620
"Huyu ni yeye, huyu ni mimi."

0:25:38.620,0:25:39.900
Ni kweli.

0:25:39.900,0:25:45.060
Haraka mlinzi anawajulisha wengine.

0:25:45.060,0:25:53.180
Anamjulisha mlinzi mkuu, "mwanafamilia wa karibu anataka kuonana na gavana"

0:25:53.180,0:26:00.880
Watamjulisha mshauri mkuu wa gavana - kwa sababu wanafanya kazi kwa maelekezo.

0:26:00.880,0:26:07.140
Mshauri atalishughulikia, "Tafadhali, jina lako ni nani? umefukuzwa kazi. mjumbe gani wa familia?"

0:26:07.140,0:26:11.420
Tunazungumzia itifaki - fikiria, kumleta mtu kutoka kijijini?

0:26:11.420,0:26:14.840
Je mtu huyu anaweza kuonana na gavana?

0:26:14.840,0:26:16.880
Hizi ni hadithi.

0:26:16.880,0:26:19.720
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:26:19.720,0:26:21.200
Uogope wakati ujao.

0:26:21.200,0:26:22.260
Mwambie jirani yako.

0:26:22.260,0:26:23.360
[Ogopa wakati ujao.]

0:26:23.360,0:26:24.500
Siwasikii.

0:26:24.500,0:26:25.860
[Ogopa wakati ujao.]

0:26:25.860,0:26:31.020
Usipoogopa wakati ujao, utaishia kusimulia hadithi.

0:26:31.020,0:26:38.900
Mwambie jirani yako, "Usipokuwa na hofu ya wakati ujao, utaishia kusimulia hadithi."

0:26:38.900,0:26:42.540
Kama baadhi ya watu, wanasimulia hadithi...

0:26:42.540,0:26:49.040
Wengi wetu hapa tuna muda wa kusimulia hadithi za rais, katibu mkuu,

0:26:49.040,0:26:57.560
jinsi mlivyoanza shule na alikuwa mdogo kwako, jinsi ulivyokuwa unamsaidia, jinsi ulivyokuwa mwanafunzi wa kwanza,

0:26:57.560,0:27:00.660
jinsi ulivyokuwa mkubwa...

0:27:00.660,0:27:02.440
Watu wanakuwa wanasikiliza.

0:27:02.440,0:27:10.080
Ukimaliza kusimulia watakuwa....

0:27:10.080,0:27:13.100
Sitaki kusimulia hadithi.

0:27:13.100,0:27:17.160
Naogopa wakati ujao.

0:27:17.160,0:27:22.620
Nikimuona mvulana mdogo amekuja kwangu, sitaki kujua historia yake.

0:27:22.620,0:27:29.940
Haijalishi ni tajiri au masikini.... kwa sababu Mungu daima yuko upande wa wale masikini.

0:27:29.940,0:27:36.720
Mara zote Mungu yupo upande wa wale wasio na kitu.

0:27:36.720,0:27:43.340
Wale watoto wadogo ninapowaona - niko makini daima.

0:27:43.340,0:27:52.660
Nahitaji kuwaambia nyie watu kwa nini niko makini daina na wakati ujao.

0:27:52.660,0:28:02.420
Mnajua kwamba Yesu anaweza akaja kama mtu kuijaribu imani yako, kuangalia uko imara kiasi gani?

0:28:02.420,0:28:05.140
Inaweza kutokea hata hapa kanisani.

0:28:05.140,0:28:12.560
Anaweza akaja na amevaa mavazi mabaya, aina ambayo huwezi kutegemea kuwaona watu wamevaa kanisani.

0:28:12.560,0:28:15.740
Ataanza jaribu lake kwa mlinzi.

0:28:15.740,0:28:20.560
"Tafadhali, nisaidie. Nataka kuabudu."

0:28:20.560,0:28:34.240
Walinzi wasipokuwa kiroho, watasema, "Tafadhali! Kabla sijafumbua macho yangu..... Tafuta njia yako!"

0:28:34.240,0:28:36.660
Nasi tupo hapa kwa ajili ya Yesu.

0:28:36.660,0:28:41.900
Yesu huyu huyu ambaye tupo hapa kwa ajili yake, ndiye yule tunayemfukuza kule nje.

0:28:41.900,0:28:45.800
Nini kitafuata?

0:28:45.800,0:28:49.360
Ukimfukuza Yesu, nini kitafuata?

0:28:49.360,0:28:51.440
Wengi wetu ...

0:28:51.440,0:28:56.200
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:28:56.200,0:28:59.460
Upo ndani ya gari zuri unaendesha....

0:28:59.460,0:29:06.780
Mtu anaweza tu kuja na kusema, "Tafadhali, sijala tangu asubuhi. Nisaidie."

0:29:06.780,0:29:09.060
Unamuangalia huyo mtu...

0:29:09.060,0:29:15.320
Hujui kwamba Mwokozi unayemwita, ndiye anayekuomba msaada.

0:29:15.320,0:29:20.080
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:29:20.080,0:29:22.600
Hujui.

0:29:22.600,0:29:30.780
Utasema, "Jinsi gani mwokozi wa ulimwengu anaweza akaja hivi hivi tu?" Hapana!

0:29:30.780,0:29:33.020
Hana mwanzo, hana mwisho.

0:29:33.020,0:29:42.460
Baada ya maombi na mambo mengine yote ambayo tumejia hapa, kuna wakati wa kuijaribu imani yako.

0:29:42.460,0:29:52.280
Jaribu hili litafanya 90% ya maksi, na 10% tu zitakuwa ni za kuja hapa

0:29:52.280,0:29:53.220
Hiyo ndiyo maana...

0:29:53.220,0:29:59.140
Chochote tunachopokea kinahitaji kuchunguzwa kwa majaribio.

0:29:59.140,0:30:02.020
Mara tu baada ya kuondoka hapa, ni wakati wa kuijaribu imani yako.

0:30:02.020,0:30:04.460
Wakati wa kupimwa unaanza hata hapa hapa.

0:30:04.460,0:30:08.100
Huo ndio uzuri.

0:30:08.100,0:30:13.440
Hakuna kitu kinachokuja bure; hakuna kitu kinachokuja kwa bahati.

0:30:13.440,0:30:18.700
Unapaswa kuwa tayari kwa mitihani itakayoijaribu imani yako.

0:30:18.700,0:30:21.120
Je, unamaanisha kile unachokisema?

0:30:21.120,0:30:23.940
Unamaanisha kile unachokifanya?

0:30:23.940,0:30:26.040
Unamaanisha kile unachokiri?

0:30:26.040,0:30:32.380
"Bwana Yesu, mimi ni mwenye dhambi, njoo maishani mwangu, ingia nafsini mwangu, unioshe kwa Damu yako ya thamani..."

0:30:32.380,0:30:36.920
Kweli unamaanisha hivyo?

0:30:36.920,0:30:43.740
Mtihani utathibitisha kama unamaanisha kile ulichokiri.

0:30:43.740,0:30:49.960
Muangalie muungwana huyu; amekuja kwa ajili ya uponyaji na fimbo ya kutembelea.

0:30:49.960,0:30:51.960
Sijui anakotoka.

0:30:51.960,0:30:56.680
Amepitia makanisa mengi, lakini yupo hapa.

0:30:56.680,0:31:00.100
Swali ambalo hua najiuliza, "Kwanini hapa?"

0:31:00.100,0:31:03.300
Hii ni kwa ajili ya kuijaribu imani yangu.

0:31:03.300,0:31:09.740
Si kwamba mimi ni bora zaidi au mzuri zaidi ya mtu mwingine lakini amekuja hapa kuijaribu imani yangu.

0:31:09.740,0:31:14.880
Ili imani yangu ijaribiwe - natakiwa kuwa wa pekee sana.

0:31:14.880,0:31:19.120
Kuwa wa pekee ni kufanya Kile ambacho Kristo anatutaka tufanye.

0:31:19.120,0:31:25.140
Sala - tumepewa neema hii ili kuomba bure na tunatakiwa kumuombea bure.

0:31:25.140,0:31:30.500
Na unatakiwa kumshukuru, kumsalim na kumbusu.

0:31:30.500,0:31:40.600
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:31:40.600,0:31:45.620
Muombee, muulize kama yuko sawa, waite wainjilisti wamhudumie.

0:31:45.620,0:31:46.880
Kama unahitaji pesa...

0:31:46.880,0:31:49.280
Labda ametumia pesa zake zote.

0:31:49.280,0:31:50.760
Sasa, yuko hapa.

0:31:50.760,0:31:58.140
Usipomsaidia kifedha ataweza kurudi duniani na yoyote uliyommfanyia yakawa bure.

0:31:58.140,0:32:05.840
Ni mtu ambaye ametumia fedha zake zote katika huu ugonjwa na yupo hapa.

0:32:05.840,0:32:07.720
Na sasa amepona.

0:32:07.720,0:32:12.300
Sasa, anahitaji kula, kwenda nyumbani, na anakuwa omba omba tena.

0:32:12.300,0:32:14.060
Hili ni jaribu lingine.

0:32:14.060,0:32:17.400
Ambalo linaweza kumpelekea kupoteza muujiza wake.

0:32:17.400,0:32:21.000
Hivyo, tafadhali; muuliza kama anahitaji usafiri.

0:32:21.000,0:32:23.820
Mwache aje tena kesho, hebu tuchangamane.

0:32:23.820,0:32:27.600
Anatakiwa aendelee kupigana vita vizuri.

0:32:27.600,0:32:30.560
Tunatakiwa kufanya chochote anachohitaji ili kumuunga mkono.

0:32:30.560,0:32:32.100
Hatakiwi kutupatia fedha.

0:32:32.100,0:32:35.800
Yeye kutoa pesa zake akiwa mgonjwa, anatupatia ugonjwa wake.

0:32:35.800,0:32:38.920
Na mimi sihitaji ugonjwa.

0:32:38.920,0:32:44.480
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:32:44.480,0:33:00.560
Kama mtu huyu ana fedha na unamwambia alipe Naira 100,000 - atakupa maramoja.

0:33:00.560,0:33:03.560
lakini fedha hizo hazijatoka moyoni mwake.

0:33:03.560,0:33:08.580
Anakupa kwa sharti: "Niponye - pokea fedha".

0:33:08.580,0:33:11.540
Huku ni kubadilishana kwa ugonjwa.

0:33:11.540,0:33:17.840
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:33:17.840,0:33:23.320
Atatoa, lakini si kutoka moyoni mwake.

0:33:23.320,0:33:25.740
Hiyo siyo sadaka.

0:33:25.740,0:33:29.880
Angenipa  kwa sharti kwamba anatakiwa kuponywa.

0:33:29.880,0:33:34.120
Ni kama kubadilishana ugonjwa na pesa.

0:33:34.120,0:33:38.240
Angenipa fedha na ugonjwa.

0:33:38.240,0:33:47.360
Ibada ya SCOAN Jumapili

0:33:47.360,0:33:53.160
Mnajua sababu ambayo sitapokea fedha moja kwa moja kutoka kwenu - hiyo ndiyo kanuni yangu.

0:33:53.160,0:33:55.520
Sitapokea fedha moja kwa moja kutoka kwako.

0:33:55.520,0:33:59.420
Kama unataka kutoa zidondoshe tu kwenye boksi au sehemu yoyote.

0:33:59.420,0:34:04.300
Na sitaki kusikia ulitoa nini.

0:34:04.300,0:34:07.020
